{{Otheruses|Wasp}}
'''''Wasp''''' was the designation given to a pair of [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] that served with the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The ships escorted ''[[Cielo]]'' as part of a [[Convoy/Legends|convoy]] containing supplies for a new base that was attacked by a force of [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] ships, including [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wings]] and the [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] ''[[Red Wind]]''. Despite the Imperial attack, they made it into [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] thanks to the efforts of [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]], flying in an [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptor]].

